{
  "texts": [
    "Hi-C read pairs were mapped with Juicer 158,159 (commit d3ee11b) and observed counts were extracted at 1 Mb resolution with Juicer Tools (commit d3ee11b).",
    "Centromeres were estimated manually in Juicebox 160 and refined with Centurion 200 v0.1.0-3-g985439c using ICE-balanced MQ ≥ 0 matrices (https://bitbucket.org/rokhsar-lab/xentr10/src/master/ hic).",
    "Rabl-like chromatin structure was visualized with PCA from Knight-Ruiz 201 -balanced MQ ≥ 30 matrices and significance was estimated by permutation testing (10,000 iterations, one-sided α = 0.01) using custom R 202 scripts.",
    "Rabl-like constraint between p-and q-arms was measured as the sum of square distances (SSD) in PC1-PC2 dimensions, calculated between nonoverlapping bins traveling sequentially away from the centromere.",
    "Inter-/intra-chromosomal contact enrichment analyses were quantified from MQ ≥ 30 matrices using χ 2 tests in R v3.5.0 (hic-analysis.R v1.0, https://bitbucket.org/rokhsar-lab/xentr10/ src/master/hic)."
  ]
}